      "description": "This Porsche 911 Carrera 4S offers a visceral driving experience powered by the legendary 3.6L flat-six engine. The M96 powerplant delivers linear torque through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, benefited by a documented IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement. Featuring the widebody architecture of the Turbo, this C4S utilizes a reinforced chassis and an all-wheel-drive system that ensures exceptional lateral grip. The suspension retains its factory composure with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings, providing communicative steering feedback through the hydraulic rack-and-pinion setup. This example represents a mechanically sound driver\u2019s car with a clean undercarriage and robust compression across all cylinders.",
